id: pm-jkjt
title: "GH-450: --duration 5m parses as 5 MONTHS — silent wrong data on meet/event/remind"
description: "Dogfood GH-450: relative-parser maps m=months (PR#263) so a 5-minute standup becomes a 5-month meeting with no warning; minutes exist as 'min' (pm-zoe4). Needs an ambiguity guard or convention flip. Duplicate check: pm-zoe4 (closed) added min granularity only; pm-o3fh moves the shortcuts but not the parser; no open overlap."
